/-- **Track forest_cd-onePI-3 (1PI).**  `SourceSubgraphExactPlus` is 1PI: it is
support-connected (Connected campaign) and bridge-free — every internal edge is
Exact or Promoted (`_internalEdge_exact_or_promoted`), and neither is a bridge
