/-- Sprint F2i-3q-4i-3b-1 helper: `PromotedInternalEdges` has positive
cardinality for any forest-type δ.  Forest-type δ has a star vertex,
which corresponds to a promoted η ∈ A_final.elements; A_final's
`HasPositiveInternalEdgesComponents` (from r.1.1.2 ∈ properDisjoint)
gives η.I.card > 0, and η.I ⊆ PromotedInternalEdges via the sum. -/
private theorem forestQuotientForestSigmaForestCoverPromotedInternalEdges_card_pos_of_forestComponent
    [IsAmbientInvariantDivergence]
    [IsDivergencePreservedByAdmissibleForestContract]
    (g : HopfGen)
